text: Centerville High School is a high school in Centerville, Ohio. Centerville High School may also refer to: * Centerville Senior High School, a high school in Centerville, Indiana * Centerville High School (Centerville, Iowa), a high school in Centerville, Iowa * Centerville High School (Louisiana), a high school in Louisiana * Centerville High School (Groveton, Texas), a high school in Texas * Centerville High School (Montana), a high school in Montana ==See also== * Centreville High School (disambiguation)
